            "role": "paragraph",
            "text": "\"We collect usage data, device information, and interaction logs to improve service quality. Data retention periods vary by data type: account data is retained for 12 months after account closure, usage logs are retained for 90 days, and payment records are retained for 7 years in accordance with financial regulations.\"",
